[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "しっかし、久しぶりに会えると思ったら\nもう雷鳴の島だっけ？　出発してたとは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00373",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "もうちょっと早く来てたらよかったなぁ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00374",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私も雷鳴の島についていきたかった。\nあいつらへの借りは、私自らの手で返したいもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00375",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "兄としては、妹が危険にさらされるのは嫌だから\n単身突入される前に合流できてよかったけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00376",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "リヒャルト兄さん……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00377",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "クレオ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00378",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私も子どもの頃、冒険に兄さんを連れてった時\n守ってあげなきゃって思ったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00379",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "ああ、子ども二人で森の奥は怖かったとも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00380",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "妹さんの尻に敷かれてるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00381",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "まあ……自慢じゃないが、剣の腕じゃ\nまったくかなわないからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00382",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そうね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00383",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "即答するなぁ。\n事実とはいえ、もうちょっと兄の威厳を……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00384",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "でもまあ、いつもは心配する側だから\n心配される側になるってのは久しぶりだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00385",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "……ありがと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00386",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "どういたしまして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00387",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "麗しき家族愛……姉様、私たちも負けてられない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00388",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "今調合いいとこだから、ちょっと待ってて。\n後でたっぷりね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00389",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "どっぷりね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00390",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "みんな仲良しが一番ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00391",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "うん……これからも一緒に頑張らないと。\nレスナたちが九偉人を倒しても、まだ敵は残ってる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00392",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "パルメ族の親玉、アウグストとザスキア……\nきっと、戦うことになるから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00393",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "……えっ？　なんでここでザスキアが？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00394",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あそっか、メーヴェさんは知らないっすよね。\nザスキアさんは、世界を管理するパルメ族の一人で――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00395",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "……あのザスキアが、そんな！？\nどこか浮世離れしている感じはあったけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00396",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ヘルトとゼロの上官みたいなものなんだよね？\nそれなら、部下の責任を取ってもらわないと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00397",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "今回は留守番でも、次はきっと大活躍。\n戦力が増えるの、大歓迎",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00398",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "うーん、何かの間違いだと思うけど……\nまぁ、直接聞くしかないわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00399",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "よし、あとは仕上げ！\nもっかい釜をかき混ぜるだけ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00400",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ねね、その仕上げって、私みたいな素人でも\nできちゃったりする？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00401",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "え？　ええ、この工程は特に錬金術の素養とか、\n必要ないっすけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00402",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "娘のする錬金術というものを、私もやってみたくて。\nクレオちゃんもやりたそうにしてたよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00403",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "もちろん、知らないことへの興味は津々、\nリヒャルト兄さん譲りの好奇心だよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00404",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "はは……でも、そうっすね。今調合してるものは\nアタシの新境地を拓くためのもの――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00405",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "今のアタシがあるのはみんながいてくれたから。\n縁ってことで手伝ってもらいたいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00406",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "もちろん、ベップもヤンネさんにも。\nロマンさんも、いいかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00407",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "大役を仰せつかってしまったな。\nもちろん、私でよければ力を貸すよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00408",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "よーし、いくわよ、クレオちゃん！\n初めての共同作業よ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00409",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "とろみがついてて結構重い……！\nこれは鍛錬になるかも！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00410",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ほんと、みんながついていてくれる。\n　そう思えたら、一歩、踏み出せるはず）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00411",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]